<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Secret Message App - README</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Mono:wght@500&display=swap');

  body {
    background: #1f1f2e;
    color: #e0dfe0;
    font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  h1, h2, h3 {
    color: #f2c1c1;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px #f2c1c1;
  }

  /* Typewriter effect for main title */
  .typewriter h1 {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-right: .15em solid #f2c1c1;
    white-space: nowrap;
    margin: 0 auto;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    animation: typing 3s steps(40, end), blink-caret .75s step-end infinite;
  }
  @keyframes typing { from { width: 0 } to { width: 100% } }
  @keyframes blink-caret { 50% { border-color: transparent; } }

  .badge-custom {
    background-color: #f2a1a1;
    color: #1f1f2e;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-right: 5px;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0% { transform: scale(1); opacity:1; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.15); opacity:0.75; }
    100% { transform: scale(1); opacity:1; }
  }

  .container { max-width: 1000px; margin-top: 50px; }
  pre {
    background: #2a2a3d;
    color: #f2c1c1;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px #f2c1c1;
  }
  li { margin-bottom: 12px; position: relative; animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards; }
  li::before { content: "⭐"; position: absolute; left: -25px; }
  @keyframes fadeInUp { 0% { opacity:0; transform: translateY(20px);} 100% { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0);} }

  .card-glow {
    background: rgba(40,35,50,0.85);
    border: 1px solid #f2c1c1;
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #f2c1c1;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .card-glow:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 0 30px #f2c1c1; }

  .download-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f2a1a1, #f2c1c1);
    color: #1f1f2e;
    font-weight: bold;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  .download-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #f2c1c1, 0 0 20px #f2a1a1;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <div class="typewriter text-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-down">
    <h1>Secret Message Web App</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="card-glow" data-aos="fade-right">
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Password-protected access</li>
      <li>Owner approval system for login requests</li>
      <li>Waiting page with animated spinner</li>
      <li>Real-time polling for approval status</li>
      <li>Feedback form to contact the developer</li>
      <li>Session-based authentication</li>
      <li>Soft dark elegant theme with smooth animations</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card-glow" data-aos="fade-left">
    <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
    <div class="mb-2">
      <span class="badge badge-custom">Node.js</span>
      <span class="badge badge-custom">Express.js</span>
      <span class="badge badge-custom">EJS</span>
      <span class="badge badge-custom">Bootstrap 5</span>
      <span class="badge badge-custom">Nodemailer</span>
      <span class="badge badge-custom">bcrypt</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-glow" data-aos="fade-right">
    <h2>Installation</h2>
    <pre>
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/secret-message-app.git
cd secret-message-app
npm install
node index.js
    </pre>
  </div>

  <div class="card-glow" data-aos="fade-left">
    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the home page in your browser</li>
      <li>Enter the password</li>
      <li>Login request is sent to the owner</li>
      <li>Wait on the "Waiting for Approval" page</li>
      <li>Once approved, access the secret message</li>
      <li>Send feedback using the form if desired</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="card-glow text-center" data-aos="zoom-in">
    <h2>Download Source Code</h2>
    <a class="mt-2" href="https://github.com/yourusername/secret-message-app/archive/refs/heads/main.zip">Download Now</a>
  </div>

  <div class="card-glow" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2>Folder Structure</h2>
    <pre>
secret-message-app/
├─ utils/
│  └─ sendmail.js
├─ views/
│  ├─ home.ejs
│  ├─ waiting.ejs
│  └─ secret.ejs
├─ index.js
└─ package.json
    </pre>
  </div>

  <div class="card-glow" data-aos="flip-left">
    <h2>Security Notes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Password hashed using bcrypt</li>
      <li>Sessions prevent unauthorized access</li>
      <li>Email notifications control approvals</li>
      <li>Pending requests expire after 15 minutes</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-5" data-aos="flip-up">
    <p>Open-source project • Soft dark elegant theme • Made with ❤️</p>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
<script>
  AOS.init({ duration: 1200, once: true });
</script>

</body>
</html>
